                <h3>Summary</h3>
                <div class="container printshow">
                    <dl>
<dt>Product Description</dt>
<dd>Iiyama ProLite XU2390HS-1 - LED monitor - 23&quot;</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="alternate">
<dt>Device Type</dt>
<dd>LED-backlit LCD monitor - 23&quot;</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt>Panel Type</dt>
<dd>IPS</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="alternate">
<dt>Aspect Ratio</dt>
<dd>Widescreen - 16:9</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt>Native Resolution</dt>
<dd>FullHD 1920 x 1080</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="alternate">
<dt>Pixel Pitch</dt>
<dd>0.265 mm</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt>Brightness</dt>
<dd>250 cd/m2</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="alternate">
<dt>Contrast Ratio</dt>
<dd>1000:1 / 5000000:1 (dynamic)</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt>Response Time</dt>
<dd>5 ms</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="alternate">
<dt>Colour Support</dt>
<dd>16.7 million colours</dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dt>Input Connectors</dt>
<dd>HDMI, DVI-D, VGA</dd>
